<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Hexo on Opoa</title><link>https://example.com/tags/hexo/</link><description>Recent content in Hexo on Opoa</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>蜀ICP备20005474号-1</copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2020 12:55:04 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://example.com/tags/hexo/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Hexo 使用 SweetAlert 美化弹窗</title><link>https://example.com/post/add-sweetalert-in-hexo/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2020 12:55:04 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/post/add-sweetalert-in-hexo/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/cover/honebami-toushirou-catanime.webp" alt="Featured image of post Hexo 使用 SweetAlert 美化弹窗" />&lt;h2 id="前言">前言
&lt;/h2>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>私密文章参考: &lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/cungudafa/article/details/104346521" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Hexo（sakura）设置文章置顶+私密文章
&lt;span style="white-space: nowrap;">
&lt;svg width=".7em" height=".7em" viewBox="0 0 21 21" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
&lt;path d="m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z" fill="currentColor" />
&lt;path d="M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z"
fill="currentColor">
&lt;/svg>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>为 Hexo 加入了私密文章功能后，密码输入错误之后弹出的浏览器自带提示框，在整个博客中显得很不协调。
&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/sweetalert.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>而接下来要添加的 &lt;a class="link" href="https://sweetalert.js.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>SweetAlert
&lt;span style="white-space: nowrap;">
&lt;svg width=".7em" height=".7em" viewBox="0 0 21 21" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
&lt;path d="m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z" fill="currentColor" />
&lt;path d="M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z"
fill="currentColor">
&lt;/svg>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/a>
，感官上就舒服得多，能给人更好的交互体验。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/sweetalert1.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="安装">安装
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在 &lt;font color=orange>themes/Sakura/layout/_partial/footer.ejs&lt;/font> 文件中加入以下代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;lt;!-- sweetalert --&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;lt;script src=&amp;#34;https://unpkg.com/sweetalert/dist/sweetalert.min.js&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>修改 &lt;font color=orange>node_modules/hexo-blog-encrypt/lib/blog-encrypt.js&lt;/font> 文件&lt;/p>
&lt;p>搜索 &lt;code>alert(WrongPassMessage)&lt;/code>，找到弹出错误密码信息的js代码段&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-js" data-lang="js">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kr">await&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">verifyContent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">hmacKey&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">decoded&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}).&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">catch&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">((&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">e&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">alert&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">wrongPassMessage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">console&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">log&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">e&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">});&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>把弹框替换为 &lt;code>SweetAlert&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-js" data-lang="js">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kr">await&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">verifyContent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">hmacKey&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">decoded&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}).&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">catch&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">((&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">e&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// alert(wrongPassMessage);
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">swal&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">({&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">text&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;密码错误！&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">icon&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;error&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">className&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;password-error&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">button&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;OK&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">});&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">console&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">log&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">e&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">});&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>在 &lt;font color=orange>themes/Sakura/source/css/style.css&lt;/font> 文件中调整弹窗的样式&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-css" data-lang="css">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c">/* 密码错误sweetalert弹框样式修改 */&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nc">swal-overlay&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">background-color&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">transparent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nc">swal-footer&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">text-align&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">center&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nc">password-error&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">box-shadow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">px&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">px&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">px&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">rgba&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">0.15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">border-radius&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">px&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;font style="color:red">&lt;b>注意：由于修改了依赖库中的代码，一旦修改或更新依赖都会覆盖掉我们的修改，需要重新修改。&lt;/b>&lt;/font>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="参考文章">参考文章
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="http://yearito.cn/posts/hexo-advanced-settings.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Hexo 搭建个人博客系列：进阶设置篇
&lt;span style="white-space: nowrap;">
&lt;svg width=".7em" height=".7em" viewBox="0 0 21 21" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
&lt;path d="m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z" fill="currentColor" />
&lt;path d="M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z"
fill="currentColor">
&lt;/svg>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hexo(Sakura) 添加在线聊天 Tidio</title><link>https://example.com/post/add-tidio-in-hexo-sakura-theme/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 20:30:45 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/post/add-tidio-in-hexo-sakura-theme/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/cover/flower-water-drops.webp" alt="Featured image of post Hexo(Sakura) 添加在线聊天 Tidio" />&lt;h2 id="前言">前言
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>一直想给博客装款在线聊天软件，综合对比下来后，选择了 &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.tidiochat.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Tidio
&lt;span style="white-space: nowrap;">
&lt;svg width=".7em" height=".7em" viewBox="0 0 21 21" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
&lt;path d="m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z" fill="currentColor" />
&lt;path d="M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z"
fill="currentColor">
&lt;/svg>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/a>
，其界面优雅简洁，支持多渠道回复，网页、Windows、安卓、IOS，关键是免费功能对普通用户完全够用，所以理论上来说是完全免费的！(白嫖使我快乐)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/tidio.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="正文">正文
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>安装起来还是比较简单的，但因为是国外的网站，访问起来会有一些慢，需要点耐心。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="注册账号">注册账号
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>访问 &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.tidio.com/panel/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Tidio
&lt;span style="white-space: nowrap;">
&lt;svg width=".7em" height=".7em" viewBox="0 0 21 21" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
&lt;path d="m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z" fill="currentColor" />
&lt;path d="M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z"
fill="currentColor">
&lt;/svg>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/a>
注册账号，一个邮箱就能搞定，非常方便。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="自定义tidio">自定义Tidio
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>进入账户界面后，可以根据自己的喜好定制，可选颜色，语言，布局，侧边栏等等。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/tidio1.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>找到账户面板的 Public Key
&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oopooa/cdn/post/tidio2.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="安装">安装
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>在主题配置文件 _config.yml 添加如下代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c"># Tidio online chat&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">tidio&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">enable&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># 替换为你的Public Key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>在 &lt;font color=orange>themes/Sakura/layout/_partial/footer.ejs&lt;/font> 中添加如下代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;lt;!-- 在线通讯Tidio --&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;lt;% if (theme.tidio.enable){ %&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;lt;script src=&amp;#34;//code.tidio.co/&amp;lt;%- theme.tidio.key %&amp;gt;.js&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;lt;% } %&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>到此 Tidio 的安装就完成了，Hexo 三连后刷新页面，在右下角就能看到效果。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hexo clean &amp;amp;&amp;amp; hexo g &amp;amp;&amp;amp; hexo s
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="参考文章">参考文章
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="http://yearito.cn/posts/hexo-advanced-settings.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Hexo 搭建个人博客系列：进阶设置篇
&lt;span style="white-space: nowrap;">
&lt;svg width=".7em" height=".7em" viewBox="0 0 21 21" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
